Pre-Game Insights: Namibia pulled off a great performance to defeat Sri Lanka on Sunday by 55 runs.
The Netherlands also secured a good win against the United Arab Emirates by three wickets.
Both Namibia and Netherlands will be keen to continue their winning run and consolidate their position in the Qualifiers points table.
Miscellaneous Highlights: An equal contest between bat and ball can be expected at the Simonds Stadium in Geelong.
The team that wins the toss will look to bowl first. 160 should be a good total at the venue.
